      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "SUMMER GOLF DESTINATIONS WORTH PACKING FOR",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Best Summer Golf Spots and the Looks to Match.</p><p>Summer is officially here and so is golf season in full swing. Whether you're staying local or chasing sunshine across state lines, we rounded up a few of our favorite golf destinations that deserve a spot on your travel radar. These courses have it all: the views, the challenge, the bragging rights, and of course, the perfect vibe for your TRENDYGOLF wardrobe.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
