    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Pinehurst, North Carolina",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>History meets hospitality. Pinehurst isn't just a resort, it's a rite of passage. From the iconic No. 2 to the Cradle short course, it's where tradition and charm collide. Pack sharp polos, lightweight layers, and versatile pieces that go from tee box to town square.</p><p><strong>What to wear</strong>: A mix of classic Americana and updated prep, performance fabrics disguised as leisurewear.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
