    "text_6": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Wherever your summer takes you (whether it's the coastal breeze of Bandon Dunes, the desert sun of Scottsdale, or somewhere halfway across the globe), make sure your golf game and your wardrobe are equally dialed in. At TRENDYGOLF, we're here to make sure you're ready for every round, every destination, and every unforgettable moment along the way. From performance-driven pieces to fashion-forward fits, we've got the gear to help you look and play your best, no matter the setting.</p><p>This season, think of golf not just as a sport, but as an experience. One that deserves the right backdrop and the right style. So go ahead, book the trip, pack the polos, and chase the game wherever it leads. We'll be right here, ready to outfit you for the journey.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
